lead_paragraph: Red Bull and Aston Martin, who are developing an Adrian Newey-designed AM-RB 001 'hypercar' incorporating Formula One technology, have extended their partnership to the end of 2017.

headline.print_headline: Red Bull and Aston Martin Extend Partnership
